        "en": "Great work‚ everyone. It was a stage overflowing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3579937294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "素敵なステージだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "with Valentine’s-style love—truly wonderful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2000006669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1750462209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1750462209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "私達もお客さんの声援から沢山の愛をもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We received so much love from the audience’s cheers as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2666673336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4833436324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ファンも、私達も、みんな幸せ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans‚ us… everyone is happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4833436324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインイベント、やって良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad we did this Valentine’s event…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1589025493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（みんなが誰に本命チョコを渡したのか気になるが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m curious about who everyone gave their true feeling Valentine chocolate to‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.395951334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今の幸せそうな彼女達に、水を差すなんて出来ないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can’t spoil their happiness right now.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.1773117376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（余計な詮索はやめておこう。みんなが幸せなら、俺は）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I should stop prying. As long as they’re happy‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1773117376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（どんな相手だろうと受け入れ……受け入れ……ぐぬぬ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ll accept it no matter who it is… accept it… ngh…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3465998416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ところで、{user}君。今夜チョコを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}. You remember your promise",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8611436837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "寮に持って来る約束ちゃんと覚えてるわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to bring the chocolates to the dorm tonight‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4479703898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4505540841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大事な話があるので、忘れずに来て下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have something important to talk about‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4505540841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "待ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so please don’t forget. We’ll be waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4065712002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9381372604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（大事な話？　まさか、みんなの好きな人を……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Something important? Don’t tell me…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9381372604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（恋人を俺に打ち明けるつもりなのか！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Are they about to tell me who they love… their partners!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1666655534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.800812959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（私生活には口出ししないようにしていたが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’ve avoided interfering in their private lives‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.800812959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピ全員に恋人がいたなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If every Sunny Peace member has a partner…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4666655534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6283867035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（一体いつからこんなことに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Since when did this happen…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6283895009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（これが世間に知られたら大変なことになるぞ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If the public finds out‚ it’ll be a disaster!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4382960154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4382960154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0999988867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……いや、なんでもない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… no‚ it’s nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.263715362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
