      "text": "俺なら大丈夫だ。しっかり寮までチョコを届けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine. I’ll make sure to bring the chocolates to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0666655534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.0145547544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（落ち着け、みんなは俺を信頼して話すつもりなんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Calm down. They’re planning to talk because they trust me.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0145547544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（だったら俺も、みんなの信頼に応えないと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Then I need to live up to that trust!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.2422416999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……しっかり俺も心の準備をして行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll prepare myself mentally before I go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.1333322201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "みんながどんな決断をしようとちゃんと受け止めるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what decisions you’ve made‚ I’ll accept them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6055754339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから信じてほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please trust me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6055754339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "何があっても、俺はみんなの味方だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what happens‚ I’m on your side!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4333322201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Later that night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0159836764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事務所に届いていたチョコを全部持って来たから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought all the chocolates that arrived at the office‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1159862196,
      "sfxList": []
